      "value": "<p>This update includes a few bug fixes.</p><p><strong>Reports</strong></p><ul><li><p>Shipping Costs would be pulled in for all-time on cost reports.\u00a0The wrong date filter was being applied to shipping costs, and this has been fixed.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Misc</strong></p><ul><li><p>Updated\u00a0the &quot;Vote on New Features&quot; link to point towards our new feature request page.</p></li></ul>",
